      <h2 class="page-header" id="conversation">Conversation</h2>

      <p class="lead">A Conversation represents the concept of a thread or channel on a messenging platform.</p>

      <h4 class="page-header">Request</h4>

      <pre>
curl -XPOST -H "Content-type: application/json" -d '{
  "conversation": {
    "platform": "messenger",
    "distinct_id": "sfs78d6fsfg7-8sdfgsdfg7d7-8gbv8b8ub"
  }
}' 'https://api.dialoganalytics.com/v1/conversations?token=XJ2ws4jZsUwHmPBfsQMj82EP'</pre>

      <h4 class="page-header">Parameters</h4>

      <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-body">
          <table class="table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Param</th>
                <th>Description</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <i>platform</i>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <strong>string</strong> <span class="label label-primary">Required</span>
                  <p>The platform on which the conversation is happening. Possible values: <code>telegram</code>, <code>messenger</code>, <code>kik</code>, <code>slack</code>, <code>line</code>, <code>skype</code>, <code>wechat</code>, <code>whatsapp</code>.</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <i>distinct_id</i>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <strong>string</strong> <span class="label label-primary">Required</span>
                  <p>A unique conversation, thread or channel ID issued by the messenging platform.</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

